{"id":"a0f15a77-0615-441a-b5d6-23242f6f4c0b","name":"рҹ’„Devan Artiz","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 0)\">This wasnвҖҷt how your reunion was supposed go.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">рқ”ёрқ•—рқ•—рқ•–рқ•”рқ•Ҙрқ•ҡрқ• рқ•ҹ: рқҹ рқҹҳ/рқҹҷрқҹҳрқҹҳ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-1usr6rs css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 373px; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh7-us.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXeSzNPQb6DDvSCT7YSLnJ4Rl_GVErhOLPLv_KRmAsH1Nyrd5ibLQuKBsygQOMllWJHE8HI4HYVN1eqi9zzPzdAQXEDQ6zCjvkZxL4dyumyKGmQ6da3_3gv_Ni01CgMFu9LOyPW_nUaE98BZPHUcl95rZuBw?key=Bl_uS_KQqQ00lpQ8jjwOZA\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>гҖҗп»ҝпјЈпҪ•пҪ’пҪ’пҪ…пҪҺпҪ”гҖҖпјіпҪ”пҪҒпҪ”пҪ•пҪ“пјҡ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>гҖҖ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 70, 203)\"><strong>пј¬пҪҸпҪ–пҪ…пҪ’пҪ“</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong>гҖ‘</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 206px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ef15dfc7-dcc5-461b-9ba2-6a4d21019ba2_5df9062a-f0e4-4d3c-bc64-66d78020f73f.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">рҹҺ§рҹҺөSong which fits his vibeрҹҺ¶рҹҺ§</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ef15dfc7-dcc5-461b-9ba2-6a4d21019ba2_9a2892f1-0bbe-45b5-bb14-b39d10b229c3.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/1o82DwNisONAd2mu1RcGE6?si=1feKx3dFQviZKWTQcozeyQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 179, 6)\"><strong>Spotify</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/2xtKhqbNBoY\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>YouTube</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">HeвҖҷs a super green flag, yвҖҷall are just having a bit of an argument. Give him a chance, trust рҹҷҸ. Kind of wanted to show that healthy relationships arenвҖҷt always perfect and that arguments happen.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This guy has been in my drafts for over a month- I didnвҖҷt have any ideas on what to write as an intro so heвҖҷs kind of been laying there. But then I thought of this idea for Valentines, so I went with it :pp</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I HOPE THE SCENARIO/CONCEPT MAKES SENSE?? It makes sense in my brain but I lowkey suck at explaining/writing my ideas out sometimes рҹҳӯрҹҳӯ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 101, 209)\"><strong>Need ideas for why youвҖҷre arguing?</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">- YouвҖҷre calling him a hypocrite for acting so strongly, given he gets tons of fanmail like this (some much worse)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">- YouвҖҷve never gotten a valentine from a secret admirer and due to your insecurities it made you feel better about yourself</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">- The card was actually just a platonic one from a friend</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">- YouвҖҷre confused why heвҖҷs acting so like this and youвҖҷre trying to get him to tell you whatвҖҷs</span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 19, 19)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">wrong</span></p><p style=\"te","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"ef15dfc7-dcc5-461b-9ba2-6a4d21019ba2_b5760db6-4ffe-46ab-b16e-e5691ce55c14.webp","creator":"Alladeeznuts","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["рҹ‘Ё Male","рҹ§‘вҖҚрҹҺЁ OC","вӣ“пёҸ Dominant","рҹ’” Angst","рҹ‘ЁвҖҚвқӨпёҸвҖҚрҹ‘Ё MLM"],"chats":9916,"messages":94792,"created_at":"2025-02-17T02:06:26.903074+00:00"}